  "texts": [
    "[14] As the computational needs of AI/ML workloads increase, dynamic resource allocation is becoming increasingly important for these applications in edge computing environments.",
    "By leveraging resources close to data sources, edge computing offers a way to effectively handle the challenges of handling massive data processing.Allocating resources is made more difficult by the changing nature of edge environments.",
    "In addition to outlining these difficulties, the paper presents a novel framework that combines several resource allocation techniques designed for AI/ML applications.",
    "By taking into consideration variables including workload characteristics, resource availability, and latency limits, this system optimizes resource distribution.",
    "The authors conducted comprehensive experiments and simulations to assess the efficacy of the framework, demonstrating that it significantly boosts performance for AI/ML workloads in edge computing environments, lowers latency, and increases resource consumption."
  ],
